    [media] r820t: better report signal strength
    
    If signal is zero, shows it as a zero, not as 0xff.
    
    Signed-off-by: Mauro Carvalho Chehab <mchehab@redhat.com>
    Tested-by: Antti Palosaari <crope@iki.fi>

